---
source: crates/carta/tests/golden_e2e.rs
expression: output
---
A plain © sign decodes in running text.

Monospace <code>&amp;</code> decodes, as do a <sub>©</sub> subscript, a <sup>®</sup> superscript, and a <s>©</s> deletion.

A link label [[start|&amp;copy;]] keeps the entity literal, and so does a &amp;copy; span and a verbatim block:

<pre>&amp;copy;
</pre>
